author: Krishna Thevar
title: Maharashtra extends lockdown till April 30: CM
description: Maharashtra extends lockdown till April 30: CMMaking the announcement, Chief Minister Uddhav Thackeray said that the lockdown can be relaxed in certain areas while on others it will become stricter.
content: Maharashtra Chief Minister Uddhav Thackeray today announced that Maharashtra will extend the lockdown at least till April 30. Addressing the presspersons, in a clear appeal he asked the citizens to be prepared for an extension beyond April 30, if the need ari… [+2324 chars]
